The Quintet included Costa Rica in its tour to celebrate its 20th anniversary of existence
“To play in Costa Rica is a dream that is realised.”
In the exclusive interview with Viva, bassist Jeff Ament of Pearl Jam says that the band is prepared to show one of their best concerts on Sunday at the National Stadium.
They were expected for more than 20 years, but the band assures that a dream will come true for them when they play in Costa Rica.
