And this without taking into account the fact that the diversity introduced by the immigrants is beneficial to the creation of ideas as well as economic growth (high percentage of immigrants among American Nobel Prize winners; Google, Intel, Paypal, eBay and Yahoo were founded by immigrants).
Migrants also make a net contribution to social systems, in the European countries at an average of approximately 1% of the total budget.
